  "Please shift to gear {gear} and slow down below 2,000 RPM.": "請排入 {gear} 檔，並減速使轉速降至 2,000 RPM 以下。",
  "Ready! Perform a Full Throttle (WOT) run on a straight.": "已就緒！請在安全直線上「全力踩滿油門」開始拉轉速。",
