  "Run duration too short ({sec}s). Gearing might be too short (high ratio). Low-gear inertial losses can underestimate horsepower. Consider tuning this gear longer (lower ratio) or using a higher gear.": "拉轉時間過短 ({sec} 秒)。齒比可能過密（齒比偏大），低檔位轉動慣量損失會低估馬力。建議將此檔齒比調小（疏齒），或改用更高一檔進行測試。",
